snippet.title: Ocmo Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Ocmo is an award-winning iOS game that challenges even hardcore gamers. Ocmo is a skill- and physics-based ninja rope platformer where you swing with tentacles through the levels, using momentum to your advantage. In the game, you are the monster, so as you discover the world, it is only natural to eat a few bunnies on the way. 

Global launchdate is November 16th 2017.
(excluding Japanese, Chinese and Korean market where we plan to release localized version later).

You can find us in Facebook, twitter, instagram and our website:
https://www.facebook.com/OcmoGame/
https://twitter.com/TeamOCMO
https://www.instagram.com/teamocmo
http://www.teamocmo.com/
